          <div class="home-buying-checklist__form-label">
            Surveyors fee
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="home-buying-checklist__form-center">
          <div class="home-buying-checklist__form-description">
            <p>A payment to a structural surveyor to check for any building issues or structural problems with the property. Fees vary depending on what type of survey you choose.</p>
            <p>Average fee: £250 - £600</p>
            <div class="home-buying-checklist__form-description--link">
